{"tid":1435731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 全部有屋企人嘅都入黎 成敗關鍵係騎刧對家嘅propaganda","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T14:30:42.000Z","uid":189739,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"00412b604df554d5990e9f4c3699496ca1753d8f","tid":1435731,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:26:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">輿論逆轉戰 成敗關鍵係騎刧對家嘅propaganda</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家對家用緊既戰術係<br />\n<br />\n1. 用內地人、黑社會同黑警強行製造衝突&mdash;&gt;<br />\n2. 單方譴責示威者&mdash;&gt;<br />\n3. 製造fake news&mdash;&gt;<br />\n4. 利用c9製造社會恐慌&mdash;&gt;<br />\n5a. c9叫囝囡唔好群埋其他手足 or<br />\n5b. 自己友為保民意而割席&mdash;&gt; <br />\n6. 重蹈雨傘覆轍<br />\n<br />\n由於呢個係個linear process，只要中間有一步唔work，成條chain就會停。而家對家係行緊第三同第四步，製造fake news，然後製造社會恐慌。呢一招有兩個重點：c9同恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n大部份C9好少接觸正常人，通常都會有一班c9 酒肉朋友，而且十分八卦。佢哋大多都唔會思考，只要c9群當中有一個人有立場，佢哋就會埋哂邊。對著老公囝囡通常都好laun黎，佢哋話一就係一，話鹿係馬就係馬，係最強spread fake news工具。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對家玩緊一招propaganda technique叫<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>「訴諸恐懼」（argumentum ad metum）</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>你要選擇甲或乙。<br />\n甲令你恐懼，所以乙是正確的。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為夢遊係暴力，所以藍衫可以脫女仔底褲，所以可以用過期催淚神經毒氣。而且當社會對示威者感到恐慌時，就會有人想重返平靜，淺黃既人就會慢慢放棄。要運動成功，我們一定要拆佢呢招。<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n1. 多d陪你屋企人，令佢聽你講多過隔離陳c9講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 當佢地send黑衫人謠言時，話佢知你個訊息係錯，我聽返黎係相反。一定要好肯定咁講，唔好話「可能係」、「好似係」，如果唔係佢地唔會信。c9習性係咁，唔好問點解。之後改佢個message做藍衫人，然後send返同樣嘅訊息出去比其他藍絲。當佢地唔知邊面至係啱，就會開始無視謠言，訴諸恐懼呢招就會慢慢唔work。optional: spread埋d末日撚message出去，聽日就有隕石，仲理鬼你d示威者。<br />\n<br />\n3. 每日send一篇大陸負面新聞佢地，一定要係d燒到埋黎個d新聞，例如賣器官、拐帶、食品安全之類，唔係燒到埋黎個d就唔洗。新聞日期唔重要，因為平時佢地都係舊文共賞，好多人亦唔識check。如果佢地check到你就話「都係啊，有冇搞錯」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度係一d template，同我做每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=xA1uwRRFzrg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxA1uwRRFzrg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=9d516c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=xA1uwRRFzrg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=3C01GFe9DS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3C01GFe9DS4&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=53c43a1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=3C01GFe9DS4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=3RMK3YboCxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3RMK3YboCxs&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=b6e58c8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=3RMK3YboCxs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=dwGPHGAtjbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdwGPHGAtjbU&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=7a1df2b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=dwGPHGAtjbU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=EOJM2Yfh6cQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEOJM2Yfh6cQ&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=5088bdad\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=EOJM2Yfh6cQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=_Xbu0Ez46DY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_Xbu0Ez46DY&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=edb3a08b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=_Xbu0Ez46DY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=fgSZWRlCIXA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfgSZWRlCIXA&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzWvf1q1qK4rBaJpe4ZKN2Es%3D&h=15347540\" target=\"_bla